-- Spot Gold Advances as Much as 0.3% to $1,370.43 Per Ounce, Erasing Decline
-- B y   S u n g w o o   P a r k
-- 2010-11-30T07:27:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-30/spot-gold-advances-as-much-as-0-3-to-1-370-43-per-ounce-erasing-decline.html
Gold for immediate delivery advanced
as much as 0.3 percent to $1,370.43 an ounce, and traded at
$1,368.60 at 3:25 p.m. in Singapore. The price has fluctuated
today, dropping 0.3 percent to $1,361.90 earlier.  To contact the reporter on this story:
